<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Admin Tools ‚Äî Backup & Restore</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; margin: 24px; }
    .wrap { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
    .row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid #aaa; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-primary { border-color: #444; }
    .note { font-size: 14px; color: #444; }
    .success { background: #e7ffe7; padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #9cd49c; border-radius: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Admin Tools</h1>
    <p class="note">Backup or restore your PitchPlan database. Download a backup weekly during the season.</p>

    <% if (typeof restored !== 'undefined' || (typeof window !== 'undefined' && new URLSearchParams(window.location.search).get('restored'))) { %>
      <div class="success">Database restored successfully.</div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>üì• Download Backup</h2>
      <p>Downloads the current SQLite database (<code>data.sqlite3</code> by default).</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/admin/backup">Download backup</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>üîÅ Restore Backup</h2>
      <p>Upload a previously saved <code>.sqlite3</code> file. This will overwrite the current database.</p>
      <form action="/admin/restore" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <input type="file" name="dbfile" accept=".sqlite3,.db,.sqlite" required />
        <button class="btn" type="submit">Upload & Restore</button>
      </form>
      <p class="note">A safety copy is saved as <code>data.sqlite3.pre-restore.bak</code> before restore.</p>
    </div>

    <p><a href="/admin">‚Üê Back to Admin</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
